model.agent.property
Class Property

java.lang.Object
  model.agent.property.Property
Direct Known Subclasses:
BooleanProperty, DependenciesProperty, HistoryProperty, LocationProperty, NumberProperty, StatusProperty, TextProperty, TimeProperty, TimeWindowProperty
public abstract class Property
extends java.lang.Object

An abstract class for holding and creating properties of an Agent. All properties must extend this class.

Author:
Gerben G. Meyer
